12.1 Notice of termination by &BANKNAVN.
:SKRSLUT.
.br
:SWISS8.
&BANKNAVN. may terminate the BS debtor agreement by giving at least two
months' notice.
.br
&BANKNAVN. may terminate the agreement without notice in the event of a
material breach of contract on the customer's part. In that case,
&BANKNAVN. will inform the customer in writing of the reason for
terminating the agreement. An example of a material breach would
be if the customer failed on several occasions to ensure there were
sufficient funds in the customer's account see clause 7.2.
